                <head>No. 476<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The United States announced on August 27 the elevation of its Legations in
                    Lebanon, Syria, and the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan to the status of Embassies.
                    (Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, September 8, 1952, page
                    379)</p>
            </div>
